{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"54ecdb3699","title":"对江西找到大盐矿报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82ebb0e99e","index":0,"year":1970,"month":9,"day":2,"articleId":"54ecdb3699"}],"tags":[{"id":"9073865ccd","name":"江西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"bb41ad343f","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一是对江西省革委会的一份报告的批语。报告中说，江西老革命根据地人民和九O九地质队职工，按照毛主席的教导，报矿、找矿、探矿，经过3个多月的奋战，今年3月30日在会昌县周田公社找到了一个大盐矿，地质储量初步计算为19亿吨。化验结果，质量较好，氨化纳97.7%。从见矿到出盐，只用了47天，结束了江西无盐的历更。自前已形成年产1.5万吨的制盐能力，并生产出食盐近千吨。在报告中“氯化钠”一词后面，毛泽东加括号写了一个批注，即本篇二。1970年9月2日，中共中央办公厅将毛泽东的批语和江西省革委会的报告一起印发给在庐山参加中共九届二中全会的同志。"}],"contents":[{"id":"968005ade9","type":"title","text":"对江西找到大盐矿报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699"},{"id":"bb41ad343f","type":"paragraph","text":"江西找到了大盐矿，储量十九亿吨，可能还不止此数。印发全会各同志。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699"},{"id":"a39cb99006","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699"},{"id":"8e1c76964d","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699"},{"id":"187016d7ac","type":"paragraph","text":"即纯盐，盐是由这两种元素化合的。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699"}],"page":{"id":"8a9bba9f03","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"54ecdb3699","start":81,"end":81}}}},"__N_SSG":true}